<br>
Jebbar this is a sorta counter productive statement.<br>
<br>
A tanks job is to Hold agro, but not do damage? Then haow the hell do they hold agro? Dancing with the mob?<br>
<br>
A warrior is a specialized Melee class that should excel at dealing damage fast and hard enough to keep the mobs attention on him. Maybe what they need to do is up the Crit rate of warriors or give warriors a Focus weapon path so they can specialivze in 1 sort of weapon type be it 1hb, 1hs, 2hb, ect. A warrior should be able to generate enough agro with thier melee skills so the mob does not go after the casters or Hybrids. Yes the soak up the damage but what good is all them HP's, and AC if you cannot generate agro with Melee and taunt? I think that warriors should have the highest skill cap with all weapons. The knights should be tied with warriors with 2hs so they can start doing Melee Dps. I dunno. Just my 2cp's<br>
